      "details": "Topic 16 \u2014 Pi + local Ollama integration pattern in 2026. How to point Pi (pi.dev) at a local Ollama instance (localhost or LAN-reachable Mac Mini / Alienware). Cover: config syntax, OpenAI-compatible endpoint expectations (`/v1/chat/completions`), recommended context-window settings, tool-calling reliability with current Ollama models, latency vs cloud, and any documented gotchas with streaming or `keep_alive`. Cite Pi docs + Ollama docs + 2026 community recipes.",
